---
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="py-24 sm:py-32 bg-surface-50/50 dark:bg-dark-layer1/50 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-brand-500/[0.03] dark:bg-brand-500/[0.02] rounded-full blur-[80px]"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-sm mb-5">
          <span class="text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-400 font-bold">04</span>
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-surface-300 dark:bg-dark-layer3"></span>
          <span class="text-surface-400 dark:text-dark-text3 tracking-wide">// sobre_mí</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="reveal text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-dark-text leading-tight">
        La persona <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 to-brand-700 dark:from-brand-300 dark:to-brand-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">detrás del código</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- About card -->
    <div class="reveal max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div data-glow class="relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-surface-200/80 dark:border-dark-border/80 bg-white dark:bg-dark-layer1 shadow-xl shadow-surface-900/[0.04] dark:shadow-black/10 overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Subtle gradient accent top -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 via-brand-600 to-accent-400"></div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <!-- Avatar -->
          <div class="shrink-0">
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 sm:w-24 sm:h-24 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 via-brand-600 to-brand-800 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/20">
                SP
              </div>
              <!-- Online indicator -->
              <div class="absolute -bottom-1 -right-1 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-green-500 border-[3px] border-white dark:border-dark-layer1"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-dark-text mb-1">
              Salvador Pérez
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400 mb-5">Full-Stack Developer · Ex-Hotelero</p>

            <div class="space-y-4 text-surface-500 dark:text-dark-text2 leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
              <p>
                Más de 10 años en operaciones hoteleras — recepción, turnos, coordinación de equipos.
                Conozco cada punto de fricción porque los viví en primera persona.
              </p>
              <p>
                Un día decidí que si la herramienta que necesitaba no existía, la iba a construir yo.
                Así nació <strong class="text-surface-700 dark:text-dark-text">Four Points</strong>: no como un ejercicio académico,
                sino como respuesta real a problemas reales.
              </p>
              <p>
                Hoy desarrollo software full-stack y comparto todo el proceso aquí, en
                <strong class="text-surface-700 dark:text-dark-text">HotelCode</strong>: el código, las decisiones
                y los errores que nadie te cuenta.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Social links -->
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <a
                href="https://github.com/bpstack"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group/link inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-surface-700 dark:text-brand-200 bg-surface-50 dark:bg-brand-950/60 border border-surface-200/80 dark:border-brand-600/40 rounded-xl hover:border-surface-300 dark:hover:border-brand-500/60 hover:bg-surface-100 dark:hover:bg-brand-900/60 hover:shadow-md shadow-surface-900/[0.03] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
              >
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
                GitHub
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 opacity-0 group-hover/link:opacity-100 group-hover/link:translate-x-0.5 transition-all" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://stackbp.es"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group/link inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-surface-700 dark:text-brand-200 bg-surface-50 dark:bg-brand-950/60 border border-surface-200/80 dark:border-brand-600/40 rounded-xl hover:border-surface-300 dark:hover:border-brand-500/60 hover:bg-surface-100 dark:hover:bg-brand-900/60 hover:shadow-md shadow-surface-900/[0.03] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
                </svg>
                Portfolio
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 opacity-0 group-hover/link:opacity-100 group-hover/link:translate-x-0.5 transition-all" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
